{"tid":568433,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"去咗馬明屋企拜年 心穎讚「未來老爺奶奶」夠晒Nice","createTime":"2018-02-21T18:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T04:57:46.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ef25ea4df3e3b90ea17d65c703fa5bcfc3f11edb","tid":568433,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T18:42:24.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】黃心穎、洪永城、湯洛雯、謝東閔及劉思希等出席新劇《丫鬟大聯盟》拜神活動，黃心穎透露預了5位數（以萬計）派開工利是，比往年多，亦笑認去年的確收入增加，望繼續進步。她說：「我新年日日開工，見人就派，避無可避啦，哈哈！（何時派雙封利是？）我冇傷風喎，哈哈！數字可以加，但雙封利是沒這麼快。」<br />\n<br />\n心穎表示已到了馬國明家中拜年，大讚馬明父母友善，但由於自己父母不在港，故馬明未有到黃家拜年。她說：「我之前回了惠州探婆婆，親戚也八卦我們的緋聞，還以為我會帶他回鄉，但我有帶他的照片給婆婆看。（何時見真人？）看看有否機會啦！」此外，談到好友梁嘉琪疑被商台監製男友劈腿，女方隨即公佈「分」訊，心穎表示有透過短訊慰問嘉琪：「看到報道也很驚訝，我也不知說甚麼好，只跟她說需要我時，我一定會在，她是個好女生，亦很堅強，希望她開心。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，在劇中飾演咸濕大小姐的劉思希，笑言不明白明朝為何有這麼咸濕的人，每逢見到異性或男家丁也春心蕩漾，又指戲中的謝東閔與湯洛雯私訂終身。她說：「平時想做而做唔到的事，呢部戲做晒，長期著住肚兜，戲中間房跟潘金蓮一樣，仲餵春藥畀謝東閔。（戲服好性感？）有啲性感，但放心節目有指引會出到街。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/22/024204_112457d38cfb1a7e629dc9d7df091032.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F22%2F024204_112457d38cfb1a7e629dc9d7df091032.jpg&h=490f4953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E5%8E%BB%E5%92%97%E9%A6%AC%E6%98%8E%E5%B1%8B%E4%BC%81%E6%8B%9C%E5%B9%B4-%E5%BF%83%E7%A9%8E%E8%AE%9A-%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E8%80%81%E7%88%BA%E5%A5%B6%E5%A5%B6-%E5%A4%A0%E6%99%92nice-091400037.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%2592%2597%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%25B1%258B%25E4%25BC%2581%25E6%258B%259C%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%25A9%258E%25E8%25AE%259A-%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%2580%2581%25E7%2588%25BA%25E5%25A5%25B6%25E5%25A5%25B6-%25E5%25A4%25A0%25E6%2599%2592nice-091400037.html&d=2oBHitOUiWjcD5z7xhq%2FdQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=74f07098\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E5%8E%BB%E5%92%97%E9%A6%AC%E6%98%8E%E5%B1%8B%E4%BC%81%E6%8B%9C%E5%B9%B4-%E5%BF%83%E7%A9%8E%E8%AE%9A-%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%86%E8%80%81%E7%88%BA%E5%A5%B6%E5%A5%B6-%E5%A4%A0%E6%99%92nice-091400037.html</a>"},{"pid":"68aff9ce38cdb711dbe5c4a2a8f8c11d01820c4e","tid":568433,"uid":123180,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T18:45:15.000Z","msg":"新年流流送個賓賓俾父母 馬明真孝子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36455dea8a809bcba133fbfd61de97c8de1c045c","tid":568433,"uid":96,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T18:47:49.000Z","msg":"平時想做而做唔到的事，呢部戲做晒，長期著住肚兜，戲中間房跟潘金蓮一樣，仲餵春藥畀謝東閔。<br />\n<br />\n人頭豬著肚兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95bd2de6cbefde3eaa621f66851e81427f7ef3c","tid":568433,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T19:38:36.000Z","msg":"Mom"},{"pid":"377cea5049b655e163317f58d008e9557a617343","tid":568433,"uid":71379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T19:53:19.000Z","msg":"唔係散撚咗咩"},{"pid":"ca41dc3f38fa8b6a114e77f537113c4dfd258d48","tid":568433,"uid":152123,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T19:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/22/024204_112457d38cfb1a7e629dc9d7df091032.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F22%2F024204_112457d38cfb1a7e629dc9d7df091032.jpg&h=490f4953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/F_BHTevMgWI/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FF_BHTevMgWI%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=01f80939&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2bb54d12d363a7c7c4c5f04df6df9a86ae1515e","tid":568433,"uid":75870,"like":0,"dis